 />"},{"pid":"980b03972d8ec604d5652fa329d02323a418b051","tid":435050,"uid":143308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:30:33.000Z","msg":"冬天一件長羽絨，抓毛褸入面著冷衫同superwarm就夠。著兩條褲同厚襪。一定要著timberland，唔係會跣死。手襪、頸巾同冷帽就一定要。<br />\n<br />\n三、四月開始我就轉著superdry, 仍然要著timberland, 因為融雪跣到爆<br />\n<br />\n利申：北過你"},{"pid":"f3e193c7528442326136ca713de856115653d00b","tid":435050,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:58:31.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n出年去瑞典半年<br />\n<br />\n咩都未買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪得佢聖誕特價先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a31b1bbaf8d2d5a04ca69d22efa39c04000f39b","tid":435050,"uid":43351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:42:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n<br />\n出年去瑞典半年<br />\n<br />\n咩都未買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪得佢聖誕特價先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無見到瑞典有過咩大特價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAmazon買好過"},{"pid":"bd87feccf9a81f5fc83a6b8e6be0bcf1a3175e90","tid":435050,"uid":46885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T19:42:36.000Z","msg":"thorogood 好似平靚唔知正唔正"}]}